<!-- * ROW 1 * --> <TR VALIGN="top">

<!-- COLUMN 1:  LEFT TEXT PROMOS --> <TD WIDTH="290">

<BR>

<STRONG>The Apple Store: Design and Publishing Solutions.</STRONG> The new Apple
Store permits individuals to customize their new G3 Power Macintosh purchases to
better meet their needs. If you're a publishing or design
professional, you may wish to take a look at some of the tips available for <A
HREF="http://www.masters.media.apple.com/news/news1.html#estorepush">customizing your
creative workstations.</A> Tips are available for:  Color Publishing, Web Authoring,
Music Production, Video Publishing, and Interactive Authoring.<BR>

<BR>

<STRONG>Gistics Tech Brief Highlights Apple Return on Investment.</STRONG>
Gistics Incorporated has produced a technology brief which examines the <A
HREF="http://www.masters.media.apple.com/news/news1.html#roi">return-on-investment
(ROI) of digital media professionals</A> and the companies employing them, in the
use of the technology that maximizes productively and creative values.<BR>

</TD>

<!-- COLUMN 2: CENTER GUTTER --> <TD WIDTH="20"> <IMG
SRC="/main/elements/spacer.gif" WIDTH="7" HEIGHT="1" ALT=""></TD>

<!-- COLUMN 3: RIGHT TEXT PROMOS --> <TD WIDTH="290">

<BR>

<STRONG>The Masters of Media Solution Provider Program.</STRONG> The <A
HREF="http://www.masters.media.apple.com/partners/">Masters of Media Solution
Provider Program</A> provides comprehensive resources for resellers, VARs, and
consultants focusing on the Design &amp; Publishing markets.<BR>

<BR>

<STRONG>The Apple OS Review Newsletter.</STRONG> Apple is offering an informative
and entertaining newsletter which provides you with the latest news on the Mac
OS, from development to delivery. If you're interested in WebObjects, Java, CHRP,
or the future of Apple, take a look at the <A
HREF="http://www.masters.media.apple.com/mac_os/">Apple OS Newsletter</A>.<BR>

</TD> </TR>

